  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nI think that [`Eth1Address`](https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/45a394e9888b98e2baac97fee2b2ee61096f0315/ethereum/spec/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/teku/spec/datastructures/eth1/Eth1Address.java#L20) should check the address checksum as defined in [EIP-55](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-55). It should warn the user if the checksum fails. Maybe only warn if we detect mixed case (at least one lowercase letter & at least one uppercase letter).",
