    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For example, given this address [`0x1Db3439a222C519ab44bb1144fC28167b4Fa6EE6`](https://etherscan.io/address/0x1db3439a222c519ab44bb1144fc28167b4fa6ee6):\r\n\r\n* There should be no warning, checksum is fine:\r\n  ```\r\n  teku --validators-proposer-default-fee-recipient=0x1Db3439a222C519ab44bb1144fC28167b4Fa6EE6\r\n  ```\r\n* There should be a warning, checksum fails (made last 'E' lowercase):\r\n  ```\r\n  teku --validators-proposer-default-fee-recipient=0x1Db3439a222C519ab44bb1144fC28167b4Fa6Ee6\r\n  ```\r\n* There should be a no warning, all uppercase:\r\n  ```\r\n  teku --validators-proposer-default-fee-recipient=0x1DB3439A222C519AB44BB1144FC28167B4FA6EE6\r\n  ```\r\n* There should be a no warning, all lowercase:\r\n  ```\r\n  teku --validators-proposer-default-fee-recipient=0x1db3439a222c519ab44bb1144fc28167b4fa6ee6\r\n  ```",
